{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"Lauren Hodge: If you were going to a restaurant and wanted a healthier option,"},{"time":3000,"text":"which would you choose, grilled or fried chicken?"},{"time":5000,"text":"Now most people would answer grilled,"},{"time":7000,"text":"and it's true that grilled chicken does contain less fat and fewer calories."},{"time":10000,"text":"However, grilled chicken poses a hidden danger."},{"time":12000,"text":"The hidden danger is heterocyclic amines --"},{"time":14000,"text":"specifically phenomethylimidazopyridine,"},{"time":16000,"text":"or PhIP --"},{"time":18000,"text":"(laughter)"},{"time":20000,"text":"which is the immunogenic or carcinogenic compound."}]},{"cues":[{"time":23000,"text":"A carcinogen is any substance or agent"},{"time":25000,"text":"that causes abnormal growth of cells,"},{"time":27000,"text":"which can also cause them to metastasize or spread."},{"time":30000,"text":"They are also organic compounds"},{"time":32000,"text":"in which one or more of the hydrogens in ammonia"},{"time":35000,"text":"is replaced with a more complex group."},{"time":37000,"text":"Studies show that antioxidants"},{"time":39000,"text":"are known to decrease these heterocyclic amines."},{"time":41000,"text":"However, no studies exist yet"},{"time":43000,"text":"that show how or why."},{"time":45000,"text":"These here are five different organizations that classify carcinogens."},{"time":48000,"text":"And as you can see, none of the organizations consider the compounds to be safe,"},{"time":51000,"text":"which justifies the need to decrease them in our diet."}]},{"cues":[{"time":54000,"text":"Now you might wonder how a 13 year-old girl could come up with this idea."},{"time":57000,"text":"And I was led to it through a series of events."},{"time":59000,"text":"I first learned about it through a lawsuit I read about in my doctor's office --"},{"time":62000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":65000,"text":"which was between the Physician's Committee for Responsible Medicine"},{"time":68000,"text":"and seven different fast food restaurants."},{"time":70000,"text":"They weren't sued because there was carcinogens in the chicken,"},{"time":73000,"text":"but they were sued because of California's Proposition 65,"},{"time":77000,"text":"which stated that if there's anything dangerous in the products"},{"time":80000,"text":"then the companies had to give a clear warning."}]},{"cues":[{"time":82000,"text":"So I was very surprised about this."},{"time":84000,"text":"And I was wondering why nobody knew more"},{"time":86000,"text":"about this dangerous grilled chicken,"},{"time":88000,"text":"which doesn't seem very harmful."},{"time":90000,"text":"But then one night, my mom was cooking grilled chicken for dinner,"},{"time":93000,"text":"and I noticed that the edges of the chicken,"},{"time":95000,"text":"which had been marinated in lemon juice, turned white."},{"time":98000,"text":"And later in biology class, I learned that it's due to a process called denaturing,"},{"time":101000,"text":"which is where the proteins will change shape"},{"time":103000,"text":"and lose their ability to chemically function."},{"time":106000,"text":"So I combined these two ideas and I formulated a hypothesis,"},{"time":109000,"text":"saying that, could possibly"},{"time":111000,"text":"the carcinogens be decreased due to a marinade"},{"time":114000,"text":"and could it be due to the differences in PH?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":116000,"text":"So my idea was born,"},{"time":118000,"text":"and I had the project set up and a hypothesis,"},{"time":120000,"text":"so what was my next step?"},{"time":122000,"text":"Well obviously I had to find a lab to work at"},{"time":124000,"text":"because I didn't have the equipment in my school."},{"time":127000,"text":"I thought this would be easy,"},{"time":129000,"text":"but I emailed about 200 different people"},{"time":131000,"text":"within a five-hour radius of where I lived,"},{"time":133000,"text":"and I got one positive response that said that they could work with me."},{"time":136000,"text":"Most of the others either never responded back,"},{"time":138000,"text":"said they didn't have the time"},{"time":140000,"text":"or didn't have the equipment and couldn't help me."},{"time":142000,"text":"So it was a big commitment"},{"time":144000,"text":"to drive to the lab to work multiple times."},{"time":147000,"text":"However, it was a great opportunity to work in a real lab --"},{"time":149000,"text":"so I could finally start my project."}]},{"cues":[{"time":151000,"text":"The first stage was completed at home,"},{"time":153000,"text":"which consisted of marinating the chicken,"},{"time":155000,"text":"grilling the chicken, amassing it"},{"time":157000,"text":"and preparing it to be transported to the lab."},{"time":160000,"text":"The second stage was completed"},{"time":162000,"text":"at the Penn State University main campus lab,"},{"time":164000,"text":"which is where I extracted the chemicals,"},{"time":166000,"text":"changed the PH so I could run it through the equipment"},{"time":168000,"text":"and separated the compounds I needed"},{"time":170000,"text":"from the rest of the chicken."},{"time":172000,"text":"The final stages, when I ran the samples"},{"time":174000,"text":"through a high-pressure"},{"time":176000,"text":"liquid chromatography mass spectrometer,"},{"time":179000,"text":"which separated the compounds and analyzed the chemicals"},{"time":182000,"text":"and told me exactly how much carcinogens I had"},{"time":184000,"text":"in my chicken."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186000,"text":"So when I went through the data, I had very surprising results,"},{"time":189000,"text":"because I found that four out of the five marinating ingredients"},{"time":192000,"text":"actually inhibited the carcinogen formation."},{"time":194000,"text":"When compared with the unmarinated chicken,"},{"time":196000,"text":"which is what I used as my control,"},{"time":199000,"text":"I found that lemon juice worked by far the best,"},{"time":201000,"text":"which decreased the carcinogens"},{"time":203000,"text":"by about 98 percent."},{"time":205000,"text":"The saltwater marinade and the brown sugar marinade"},{"time":208000,"text":"also worked very well,"},{"time":210000,"text":"decreasing the carcinogens by about 60 percent."},{"time":212000,"text":"Olive oil slightly decreased the PhIP formation,"},{"time":215000,"text":"but it was nearly negligible."},{"time":217000,"text":"And the soy sauce results were inconclusive"},{"time":219000,"text":"because of the large data range,"},{"time":221000,"text":"but it seems like soy sauce"},{"time":223000,"text":"actually increased the potential carcinogens."}]},{"cues":[{"time":225000,"text":"Another important factor that I didn't take into account initially"},{"time":227000,"text":"was the time cooked."},{"time":229000,"text":"And I found that if you increase the time cooked,"},{"time":231000,"text":"the amount of carcinogens rapidly increases."},{"time":234000,"text":"So the best way to marinate chicken, based on this,"},{"time":237000,"text":"is to, not under-cook,"},{"time":239000,"text":"but definitely don't over-cook and char the chicken,"},{"time":241000,"text":"and marinate in either lemon juice, brown sugar or saltwater."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":251000,"text":"Based on these findings, I have a question for you."},{"time":254000,"text":"Would you be willing to make a simple change in your diet"},{"time":257000,"text":"that could potentially save your life?"},{"time":259000,"text":"Now I'm not saying that if you eat grilled chicken that's not marinated,"},{"time":261000,"text":"you're definitely going to catch cancer and die."},{"time":263000,"text":"However, anything you can do"},{"time":265000,"text":"to decrease the risk of potential carcinogens"},{"time":267000,"text":"can definitely increase the quality of lifestyle."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270000,"text":"Is it worth it to you?"},{"time":272000,"text":"How will you cook your chicken now?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":274000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":290000,"text":"Shree Bose: Hi everyone. I'm Shree Bose."},{"time":292000,"text":"I was the 17-18 year-old age category winner"},{"time":294000,"text":"and then the grand prize winner."},{"time":297000,"text":"And I want all of you"},{"time":299000,"text":"to imagine a little girl"},{"time":301000,"text":"holding a dead blue spinach plant."},{"time":304000,"text":"And she's standing in front of you and she's explaining to you"},{"time":307000,"text":"that little kids will eat their vegetables"},{"time":309000,"text":"if they're different colors."},{"time":311000,"text":"Sounds ridiculous, right."},{"time":313000,"text":"But that was me years ago."},{"time":315000,"text":"And that was my first science fair project."},{"time":318000,"text":"It got a bit more complicated from there."},{"time":321000,"text":"My older brother Panaki Bose"},{"time":323000,"text":"spent hours of his time explaining atoms to me"},{"time":326000,"text":"when I barely understood basic algebra."},{"time":329000,"text":"My parents suffered through many more of my science fair projects,"},{"time":332000,"text":"including a remote controlled garbage can."}]},{"cues":[{"time":334000,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":336000,"text":"And then came the summer after my freshman year,"},{"time":339000,"text":"when my grandfather passed away due to cancer."},{"time":342000,"text":"And I remember watching my family go through that"},{"time":344000,"text":"and thinking that I never wanted another family"},{"time":347000,"text":"to feel that kind of loss."},{"time":350000,"text":"So, armed with all the wisdom"},{"time":352000,"text":"of freshman year biology,"},{"time":354000,"text":"I decided I wanted to do cancer research"},{"time":357000,"text":"at 15."},{"time":359000,"text":"Good plan."},{"time":361000,"text":"So I started emailing all of these professors in my area"},{"time":363000,"text":"asking to work under their supervision in a lab."},{"time":367000,"text":"Got rejected by all except one."},{"time":369000,"text":"And then went on, my next summer,"},{"time":371000,"text":"to work under Dr. Basu"},{"time":373000,"text":"at the UNT Health Center at Fort Worth, Texas."},{"time":376000,"text":"And that is where the research began."}]},{"cues":[{"time":379000,"text":"So ovarian cancer"},{"time":381000,"text":"is one of those cancers that most people don't know about,"},{"time":384000,"text":"or at least don't pay that much attention to."},{"time":387000,"text":"But yet, it's the fifth leading cause of cancer deaths"},{"time":390000,"text":"among women in the United States."},{"time":393000,"text":"In fact, one in 70 women"},{"time":395000,"text":"will be diagnosed with ovarian cancer."},{"time":397000,"text":"One in 100"},{"time":399000,"text":"will die from it."},{"time":401000,"text":"Chemotherapy, one of the most effective ways"},{"time":403000,"text":"used to treat cancer today,"},{"time":405000,"text":"involves giving patients really high doses of chemicals"},{"time":407000,"text":"to try and kill off cancer cells."}]},{"cues":[{"time":410000,"text":"Cisplatin is a relatively common"},{"time":412000,"text":"ovarian cancer chemotherapy drug --"},{"time":415000,"text":"a relatively simple molecule made in the lab"},{"time":418000,"text":"that messes with the DNA of cancer cells"},{"time":420000,"text":"and causes them to kill themselves."},{"time":422000,"text":"Sounds great, right?"},{"time":424000,"text":"But here's the problem:"},{"time":426000,"text":"sometimes patients become resistant to the drug,"},{"time":429000,"text":"and then years after they've been declared to be cancer free,"},{"time":432000,"text":"they come back."},{"time":434000,"text":"And this time, they no longer respond to the drug."},{"time":436000,"text":"It's a huge problem."},{"time":438000,"text":"In fact, it's one of the biggest problems"},{"time":440000,"text":"with chemotherapy today."}]},{"cues":[{"time":442000,"text":"So we wanted to figure out"},{"time":444000,"text":"how these ovarian cancer cells are becoming resistant"},{"time":447000,"text":"to this drug called Cisplatin."},{"time":449000,"text":"And we wanted to figure this out,"},{"time":451000,"text":"because if we could figure that out,"},{"time":453000,"text":"then we might be able to prevent that resistance from ever happening."},{"time":456000,"text":"So that's what we set out to do."},{"time":458000,"text":"And we thought it had something to do with this protein called AMP kinase,"},{"time":461000,"text":"an energy protein."},{"time":463000,"text":"So we ran all of these tests blocking the protein,"},{"time":466000,"text":"and we saw this huge shift."},{"time":468000,"text":"I mean, on the slide, you can see"},{"time":470000,"text":"that on our sensitive side,"},{"time":472000,"text":"these cells that are responding to the drug,"},{"time":474000,"text":"when we start blocking the protein,"},{"time":476000,"text":"the number of dying cells -- those colored dots --"},{"time":479000,"text":"they're going down."},{"time":481000,"text":"But then on this side, with the same treatment,"},{"time":484000,"text":"they're going up -- interesting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":487000,"text":"But those are dots on a screen for you;"},{"time":489000,"text":"what exactly does that mean?"},{"time":491000,"text":"Well basically that means"},{"time":493000,"text":"that this protein is changing"},{"time":495000,"text":"from the sensitive cell to the resistant cell."},{"time":497000,"text":"And in fact, it might be changing the cells themselves"},{"time":501000,"text":"to make the cells resistant."},{"time":504000,"text":"And that's huge."},{"time":506000,"text":"In fact, it means that if a patient comes in"},{"time":508000,"text":"and they're resistant to this drug,"},{"time":510000,"text":"then if we give them a chemical to block this protein,"},{"time":513000,"text":"then we can treat them again"},{"time":515000,"text":"with the same drug."},{"time":517000,"text":"And that's huge for chemotherapy effectiveness --"},{"time":520000,"text":"possibly for many different types of cancer."},{"time":524000,"text":"So that was my work,"},{"time":526000,"text":"and it was my way of reimagining the future"},{"time":529000,"text":"for future research, with figuring out exactly what this protein does,"},{"time":533000,"text":"but also for the future of chemotherapy effectiveness --"},{"time":536000,"text":"so maybe all grandfathers with cancer"},{"time":539000,"text":"have a little bit more time to spend with their grandchildren."}]},{"cues":[{"time":542000,"text":"But my work wasn't just about the research."},{"time":546000,"text":"It was about finding my passion."},{"time":549000,"text":"That's why being the grand prize winner"},{"time":551000,"text":"of the Google Global Science Fair --"},{"time":553000,"text":"cute picture, right --"},{"time":555000,"text":"it was so exciting to me and it was such an amazing honor."},{"time":558000,"text":"And ever since then,"},{"time":560000,"text":"I've gotten to do some pretty cool stuff --"},{"time":562000,"text":"from getting to meet the president"},{"time":564000,"text":"to getting to be on this stage"},{"time":566000,"text":"to talk to all of you guys."}]},{"cues":[{"time":568000,"text":"But like I said, my journey wasn't just about the research,"},{"time":571000,"text":"it was about finding my passion,"},{"time":573000,"text":"and it was about making my own opportunities"},{"time":575000,"text":"when I didn't even know what I was doing."},{"time":578000,"text":"It was about inspiration"},{"time":580000,"text":"and determination"},{"time":582000,"text":"and never giving up on my interest"},{"time":584000,"text":"for science and learning and growing."},{"time":587000,"text":"After all, my story begins"},{"time":590000,"text":"with a dried, withered spinach plant"},{"time":592000,"text":"and it's only getting better from there."}]},{"cues":[{"time":594000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":596000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":608000,"text":"Naomi Shah: Hi everyone. I'm Naomi Shah,"},{"time":611000,"text":"and today I'll be talking to you about my research"},{"time":613000,"text":"involving indoor air quality"},{"time":615000,"text":"and asthmatic patients."},{"time":617000,"text":"1.6 million deaths worldwide."},{"time":620000,"text":"One death every 20 seconds."},{"time":623000,"text":"People spend over 90 percent of their lives indoors."},{"time":627000,"text":"And the economic burden of asthma"},{"time":629000,"text":"exceeds that of HIV and tuberculosis combined."},{"time":632000,"text":"Now these statistics had a huge impact on me,"},{"time":635000,"text":"but what really sparked my interest in my research"},{"time":638000,"text":"was watching both my dad and my brother"},{"time":640000,"text":"suffer from chronic allergies year-round."},{"time":642000,"text":"It confused me;"},{"time":644000,"text":"why did these allergy symptoms persist"},{"time":646000,"text":"well past the pollen season?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":648000,"text":"With this question in mind, I started researching,"},{"time":651000,"text":"and I soon found that indoor air pollutants were the culprit."},{"time":654000,"text":"As soon as I realized this,"},{"time":656000,"text":"I investigated the underlying relationship"},{"time":658000,"text":"between four prevalent air pollutants"},{"time":660000,"text":"and their affect on the lung health of asthmatic patients."},{"time":663000,"text":"At first, I just wanted to figure out"},{"time":666000,"text":"which of these four pollutants have the largest negative health impact"},{"time":669000,"text":"on the lung health of asthmatic patients."},{"time":672000,"text":"But soon after, I developed a novel mathematical model"},{"time":675000,"text":"that essentially quantifies the effect"},{"time":677000,"text":"of these environmental pollutants"},{"time":680000,"text":"on the lung health of asthmatic patients."},{"time":682000,"text":"And it surprises me"},{"time":684000,"text":"that no model currently exists"},{"time":686000,"text":"that quantifies the effect of environmental factors"},{"time":688000,"text":"on human lung health,"},{"time":690000,"text":"because that relationship seems so important."}]},{"cues":[{"time":693000,"text":"So with that in mind,"},{"time":695000,"text":"I started researching more, I started investigating more,"},{"time":697000,"text":"and I became very passionate."},{"time":699000,"text":"Because I realized"},{"time":701000,"text":"that if we could find a way to target remediation,"},{"time":703000,"text":"we could also find a way"},{"time":705000,"text":"to treat asthmatic patients more effectively."},{"time":709000,"text":"For example, volatile organic compounds"},{"time":711000,"text":"are chemical pollutants"},{"time":713000,"text":"that are found in our schools, homes and workplaces."},{"time":715000,"text":"They're everywhere."},{"time":717000,"text":"These chemical pollutants"},{"time":719000,"text":"are currently not a criteria air pollutant,"},{"time":721000,"text":"as defined by the U.S. Clean Air Act."},{"time":723000,"text":"Which is surprising to me,"},{"time":725000,"text":"because these chemical pollutants, through my research,"},{"time":727000,"text":"I show that they had a very large negative impact"},{"time":730000,"text":"on the lung health of asthmatic patients"},{"time":732000,"text":"and thus should be regulated."}]},{"cues":[{"time":734000,"text":"So today I want to show you"},{"time":736000,"text":"my interactive software model that I created."},{"time":739000,"text":"I'm going to show it to you on my laptop."},{"time":741000,"text":"And I have a volunteer subject in the audience today,"},{"time":743000,"text":"Julie."},{"time":745000,"text":"And all of Julie's data has been pre-entered"},{"time":748000,"text":"into my interactive software model."},{"time":750000,"text":"And this can be used by anyone."},{"time":752000,"text":"So I want you to imagine that you're in Julie's shoes,"},{"time":754000,"text":"or someone who's really close to you"},{"time":756000,"text":"who suffers from asthma or another lung disorder."},{"time":759000,"text":"So Julie's going to her doctor's office"},{"time":761000,"text":"to get treated for her asthma."},{"time":763000,"text":"And the doctor has her sit down,"},{"time":765000,"text":"and he takes her peak expiratory flow rate --"},{"time":768000,"text":"which is essentially her exhalation rate,"},{"time":770000,"text":"or the amount of air that she can breathe out in one breath."}]},{"cues":[{"time":773000,"text":"So that peak expiratory flow rate,"},{"time":775000,"text":"I've entered it up into the interactive software model."},{"time":777000,"text":"I've also entered in her age, her gender and her height."},{"time":780000,"text":"I've assumed that she lives in an average household"},{"time":782000,"text":"with average air pollutant levels."},{"time":784000,"text":"So any user can come in here"},{"time":786000,"text":"and click on \"lung function report\""},{"time":788000,"text":"and it'll take them to this report that I created."},{"time":790000,"text":"And this report really drives home the crux of my research."}]},{"cues":[{"time":794000,"text":"So what it shows -- if you want to focus on that top graph in the right-hand corner --"},{"time":798000,"text":"it shows Julie's actual peak expiratory flow rate"},{"time":800000,"text":"in the yellow bar."},{"time":802000,"text":"This is the measurement that she took in her doctor's office."},{"time":805000,"text":"In the blue bar at the bottom of the graph,"},{"time":807000,"text":"it shows what her peak expiratory flow rate,"},{"time":810000,"text":"what her exhalation rate or lung health, should be"},{"time":812000,"text":"based on her age, gender and height."},{"time":815000,"text":"So the doctor sees this difference between the yellow bar and the blue bar,"},{"time":818000,"text":"and he says, \"Wow, we need to give her steroids,"},{"time":821000,"text":"medication and inhalers.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":824000,"text":"But I want everyone here to reimagine a world"},{"time":827000,"text":"where instead of prescribing steroids,"},{"time":829000,"text":"inhalers and medication,"},{"time":831000,"text":"the doctor turns to Julie and says,"},{"time":833000,"text":"\"Why don't you go home and clean out your air filters."},{"time":835000,"text":"Clean out the air ducts in your home,"},{"time":837000,"text":"in your workplace, in your school."},{"time":839000,"text":"Stop the use of incense and candles."},{"time":842000,"text":"And if you're remodeling your house,"},{"time":844000,"text":"take out all the carpeting and put in hardwood flooring.\""},{"time":847000,"text":"Because these solutions are natural,"},{"time":849000,"text":"these solutions are sustainable,"},{"time":851000,"text":"and these solutions are long-term investments --"},{"time":854000,"text":"long-term investments that we're making"},{"time":856000,"text":"for our generation and for future generations."},{"time":858000,"text":"Because these environmental solutions"},{"time":861000,"text":"that Julie can make in her home, her workplace and her school"},{"time":864000,"text":"are impacting everyone that lives around her."}]},{"cues":[{"time":867000,"text":"So I'm very passionate about this research"},{"time":869000,"text":"and I really want to continue it"},{"time":871000,"text":"and expand it to more disorders besides asthma,"},{"time":874000,"text":"more respiratory disorders, as well as more pollutants."},{"time":877000,"text":"But before I end my talk today,"},{"time":879000,"text":"I want to leave you with one saying."},{"time":881000,"text":"And that saying is that genetics loads the gun,"},{"time":884000,"text":"but the environment pulls the trigger."},{"time":886000,"text":"And that made a huge impact on me"},{"time":888000,"text":"when I was doing this research."},{"time":890000,"text":"Because what I feel, is a lot of us think"},{"time":892000,"text":"that the environment is at a macro level,"},{"time":895000,"text":"that we can't do anything to change our air quality"},{"time":897000,"text":"or to change the climate or anything."}]},{"cues":[{"time":900000,"text":"But if each one of us takes initiative in our own home,"},{"time":903000,"text":"in our own school and in our own workplace,"},{"time":906000,"text":"we can make a huge difference in air quality."},{"time":908000,"text":"Because remember, we spend 90 percent of our lives indoors."},{"time":912000,"text":"And air quality and air pollutants"},{"time":915000,"text":"have a huge impact on the lung health of asthmatic patients,"},{"time":918000,"text":"anyone with a respiratory disorder"},{"time":920000,"text":"and really all of us in general."}]},{"cues":[{"time":922000,"text":"So I want you to reimagine a world"},{"time":924000,"text":"with better air quality,"},{"time":926000,"text":"better quality of life"},{"time":928000,"text":"and better quality of living for everyone"},{"time":930000,"text":"including our future generations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":932000,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":934000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":941000,"text":"Lisa Ling: Right."},{"time":943000,"text":"Can I have Shree and Lauren come up really quickly?"},{"time":948000,"text":"Your Google Science Fair champions."},{"time":950000,"text":"Your winners."}]},{"cues":[{"time":952000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}